description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 1.2 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Room Air Cleaners that are effective as of July 1, 2004. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=room_airclean.pr_crit_room_airclean
